# AgainERP — Common Rules

**Read first:** `docs/BRAIN.md` → stop at lowest [AI Reading Policy](./docs/BRAIN.md#ai-reading-policy) level for your task.  
**Deep dive:** `docs/00-foundation/PROJECT_BRAIN.md` · **Full spec:** `docs/00-foundation/PROJECT_COMMON_RULES.md`

## Modules
- **Core** (Users, RBAC, Tenant, Contacts, Workflow, Events) = always on.
- **Business/Industry** (Inventory, Manufacturing, CRM, …) = optional per tenant/plan.
- **Module off must not break others:** no cross-module DB; Services/Events/APIs only; graceful UI hide (no crash).
- Declare deps in `ModuleManifest.md` + `docs/01-architecture/MODULE_DEPENDENCY_MAP.md`.

## SaaS & scale
- Multi-tenant (`tenant_id`); API-first `/api/v1/{module}/`; modules independently developable/deployable.
- New module → full docs package under `docs/03-business-modules/{module}/` before code.

## UI (prototype & product)
- **DataTable (MANDATORY):** Every entity list page MUST use the Product List AG Grid pattern — `product-grid.tsx` · [datatable-and-drawer-standard.md](docs/04-uiux/standards/datatable-and-drawer-standard.md). Custom `<table>` or `<div>`-based lists are **forbidden** for entity lists.
- **CRUD = List page + right Sheet drawer** — `?create=1` · `?view={id}` · `?edit={id}` (view/create/edit **all in drawer**)
- **Never** `/new` or `/[id]/edit` routes for standard entity CRUD. Reference: `/catalog/products`.
- **Mobile-first mandatory:** full-width drawer on small screens, AG Grid → card fallback on mobile, 44px tap targets.

## Dark mode (mandatory — always consider)
- Use `useIsDark()` hook → toggle `ag-theme-quartz-dark` on AG Grid containers.
- All colors MUST use Tailwind/shadcn CSS variables (`bg-card`, `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border`, `muted`, etc.) — **never hardcode** `bg-white`, `text-gray-900`, or any fixed light color.
- Icons, badges, charts, sheets, and all UI must look correct in **both** light and dark mode before shipping.
- Recharts: use `fill="currentColor"` or CSS-variable stroke/fill; never hardcode hex colors.

## Documentation-first
- New plan/feature → update `Architecture.md`, build guide, `MODULE_DEPENDENCY_MAP.md`, `CHANGELOG.md` **before** code.
- Docs status **Ready** per `docs/00-foundation/GOVERNANCE.md` / `docs/00-foundation/PRE_CODE_GATE.md`.

## Code
- Zustand: never `.slice()`/`.filter()` inside selectors (causes infinite re-render).
- Recharts: never type Tooltip `formatter` param as `number` — use `@/lib/charts/recharts-tooltip` or `(v) => Number(v ?? 0)`. See `docs/04-uiux/standards/recharts-conventions.md`.
- Minimal focused diffs; match existing conventions.
